    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/yhORLf3xG56C1lj3vRthHaDvRfQ=/0x0:1000x667/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73754751/Hoto_3.6V_Electric_Screwdriver_Kit_Lifestyle_Main_Image.10.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;Because everyone loves an electric screwdriver.&lt;/em&gt; | Image: Hoto&lt;/figcaption&gt;
